# $200M ARR is achievable in 36 months through three conversion phases
@type: timeline

@step: Months 1–6 | Foundation | Usage analytics, payment infrastructure, feature wall instrumentation
@step: Months 7–15 | Freemium Launch | Gated premium tier, email conversion campaigns, in-app upsell triggers
@step: Months 16–24 | Expansion | Usage-based add-ons, team/enterprise plans, annual billing incentives
@step: Months 25–36 | $200M ARR | 180K paid subscribers × $1,100 avg ARR

@source: BCG analysis based on comparable freemium monetization trajectories, 2024

@notes: The 180K paid subscriber target requires a 4.3% conversion rate on the current MAU base. This is achievable but demands relentless funnel optimization throughout Phase 2.

